Output assets/quick_start_1.gif
Require dart
Set Margin 0
Set BorderRadius 0
Set WindowBar ""
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 950
Set Height 180
Set Padding 10
Set Theme "OneDark"

Hide
Type "clear && dart run example/quick_start_1.dart"
Enter
Show

Sleep 1s
Type "my_awesome_app"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 1s
Right
Sleep 500ms
Left
Sleep 500ms

Sleep 1s
